reviewText: What can I say that I already haven't said about season 1! This web series absolutely rocks! The entire cast show dedication with this series and Mr. Fernandez continues to amaze us with the stories and effects! From the Web series to the comic books BODY JUMPERS is a win in every way, I had a chance to meet some of the actors in person at a convention  along with Mr. Fernandez and family, He and Gisele are super cool individuals who are working hard to bring us quality entertainment, wonderful people who are dedicated to the cause! Body Jumpers entire cast members really entertain and their hard work shows, each one of them!  I am looking forward to getting this DVD as soon as it ships! Body Jumpers keep it going, you guys are awesome!
